        "timestamp": "2020-03-04 12:34:33.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nHello,\nI've got two questions on this patch:\n\n* there's a tomcat server AND a mysql server on the same container?\n* onap user shouldn't have passwordless sudo capabilities",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
      {
        "id": "622c4d6c5bd5afb9a4fece4ea53fe03d385711e8",
        "author": {
          "account_id": 925,
          "name": "Yan Yang",
          "display_name": null,
          "email": "yangyanyj@chinamobile.com",
          "username": "yangyan"
        },
        "author_role": "OWNER",
        "timestamp": "2020-03-04 15:28:32.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nhi Sylvain Desbureaux, this component is contributed by vendor, \nthere's a tomcat server AND a mysql server on the same container? Yes\nonap user shouldn't have passwordless sudo capabilities - we add sudo capabilties to ensure have start mysql permission.\n\nBecause the componnents owner no longer maintain this, so we just make the modification while avoiding affecting the original logic and design.",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
      {
        "id": "bbf1f74c83efa4d90a7e095a5baf8c67cc6832c0",
        "author": {
          "account_id": 2319,
          "name": "Sylvain Desbureaux",
