        "timestamp": "2020-03-04 17:19:06.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nStrongly agree with Sylvain. If there is no one to maintain it and there is no dependency it should be removed.\n\nAs for the root part. You are solving troubles that you created on your own. Just don;t put mysql DB in your container image and you won't need root permissions",
